Package: readabilityes
Title:  Provides functions to calculate readability metrics for Spanish
  texts, including sentence, word, and syllable counts, syllabification, and
  common readability indexes such as FernÃ¡ndez-Huerta, INFLESZ, and
  Szigriszt-Pazos. Includes text cleaning, tokenization, and utilities to
  handle accented characters and Spanish-specific orthographic rules.
